6. Technical Logic (High Level)
The Algorithm: The backend must run a logic script every night (or upon request) that checks: When did the user last see this card? What did they rate it? Is it due today?

Image Optimization: Because this is a "Visual Representation" site, the system needs to serve high-quality images that load instantly (Lazy loading).

Mobile First: 70% of users will study on their commute. The flashcard interface must work perfectly on a phone screen.